('hav-dhmjcfpf080', 'DHMJCFPF080', 'Havells Higher Rating MCB FP — 80 A', 'Havells', 'Switchgear', 'Circuit Breaker · Imported By Havells India Ltd. · Execution pole Four Pole (FP) · Type C Curve · Rating 125 A', 11450, 6733, 'pc', 'https://havells.com/media/catalog/product/cache/74c1057f7991b4edb2bc7bdaa94de933/import/Switchgear/DHMJCFPF080.jpg', '{"Rating":"80 A"}'::jsonb, 'DHMJCFPF080', null, '{"source":"havells.com","description":"125 A","key_features":["Application : For industrial and commercial purposes","Rating : 80 A to 125 A","Specification : IS/IEC 60947-2","Note: Product images are for illustrative purposes and may differ from the actual product"],"features":[{"title":"Trip Free mechanism","body":"A circuit-breaker, the moving contacts of which return to and remain in the open position when the automatic opening operation is initiated after the initiation of the closing operation, even if the closing command is maintained."},{"title":"Positive Contact Indication","body":"It clearly indicates contact position through flag indication (Red-ON,Green-OFF) thus enhancing safety."},{"title":"Thermal and Magnetic trip function with Hammer trip operation","body":"The thermal operation provides protection from moderate overloads.under overload condition,a thermometallic element(bimetallic strip) deflects until it operates a latching mechanism allowing the main conatcts to open. In magnetic operation, large overloads or short circuit current actuates a solenoid causing a plunger to strike the latching mechanism rapidly opening the main contacts."},{"title":"Current Limiting design for short circuit fault protection","body":"In a current limiting breaker,the tripping & arc control mechanism are so designed that under short circuit conditions,the contacts are physically separated and the electodynamic forces set up by fault current, assist the extinction is less than half cycle."}],"specs":{"Imported By":"Havells India Ltd.","Country Of Origin":"China","Execution pole":"Four Pole (FP)","Type":"C Curve","Rating":"125 A","Net Quantity":"1 N","Product range":"Circuit Breaker"}}'::jsonb, true),
